              .p-6
                .mb-4
                  h3.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.group-hover:text-purple-900.transition-colors.duration-300 STLs & Mounts
                  span.text-sm.text-gray-500.group-hover:text-purple-600.transition-colors.duration-300 3D Printing
                p.text-gray-600.mb-4.group-hover:text-gray-700.transition-colors.duration-300 Download 3D printable mounts, cases, and accessories for your Baldrick Boards.
                ul.text-sm.text-gray-600.mb-4.space-y-1.group-hover:text-gray-700.transition-colors.duration-300
                  li • 3D printable mounts
                  li • Protective cases
                  li • Mounting brackets
                  li • Custom accessories

          / Board Dimensions
